{"tid":1627031,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中銀㩒唔到錢:-(","createTime":"2019-10-05T14:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T15:21:18.000Z","uid":109251,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"234c037c3242fbafe83b119f4afbb0ef09146fcf","tid":1627031,"uid":109251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日想㩒哂中銀所有錢走資 <br />\n落到樓下先發現 打爆既打爆 無打爆就被人㩒哂啲錢<br />\n而家想走資太遲 <br />\n我知道前線想香港有好既將來<br />\n但係希望唔好失控<br />\n除咗會影響民生令憎既人更憎 分化更化<br />\n政府只會視反對者係叛亂者 <br />\n<br />\n可能我講既野好唔啱聽 不過呢段時間心情真係好矛盾<br />\n尤其工作 家庭都圍繞住政治、中國 <br />\n屋企人食飯一直嘈交 (老母極藍 文革地主老豆極黃）<br />\n公司同事互相用政治terms搞gag <br />\n香港環境又忽然多咗好多講鄉下話既大陸人<br />\n(我啱啱回流香港)<br />\n搞到我越嚟越焦慮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我打咁多嘢其實係想問呢段時間中銀atm係咪唔會再有錢㩒<br />\n同埋想知清楚打爆中銀 藍店既目的係乜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好屌我"},{"pid":"914383ecbddd3d33cb6f982304aa48478dcb2ba8","tid":1627031,"uid":24306,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用銀通櫃員機"},{"pid":"65e4888e56e8625ec79bafd65855b526a91239ef","tid":1627031,"uid":60200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"234c037c3242fbafe83b119f4afbb0ef09146fcf","tid":1627031,"uid":109251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日想㩒哂中銀所有錢走資 <br />\n落到樓下先發現 打爆既打爆 無打爆就被人㩒哂啲錢<br />\n而家想走資太遲 <br />\n我知道前線想香港有好既將來<br />\n但係希望唔好失控<br />\n除咗會影響民生令憎既人更憎 分化更化<br />\